                <br><br>
            </div>
            </a>
        </div> <br> <br>
        <span style="font-family:Changa;font-size: 200%;">Product and Public</span> <br> <br>
        <div style="display:inline;">
            <a href="/join/marketing">
            <div class="box">
                <h3>Marketing</h3>
                <span>Help us with advertisements and deciding what's best.</span>
                <br><br>
            </div>
            </a>
            <a href="/join/social-media">
            <div class="box">
                <h3>Social Media Coordinator</h3>
                <span>Decide what we post and interact with the people.</span>
